FixedSizeTable[K; V] = object
  capacity: uint
  used: Atomic[uint]
  recycle: RingBuffer[DenseIdx]
  dense: ptr UncheckedArray[Entry[K, V]]
  sparse: ptr UncheckedArray[AtomicDenseIdx]
Lock-free table of values that wont ever resize
